{"tid":2404786,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"美國智庫CSIS討論如何以突襲手段，在與中國或俄國的大國衝突上取得優勢。","createTime":"2021-02-12T02:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T07:58:09.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d80c6da04b275e1d7d6265764cd04d5f9eba46f","tid":2404786,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:43:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/UnitedHK18/5975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUnitedHK18%2F5975&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGcwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=68f1846f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/UnitedHK18/5975</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VzqswBH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVzqswBH.jpg&h=cc7abb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拜登上台不到一個月，CSIS智庫上月發表報告，討論美國如何以&ldquo;突襲&rdquo;手段，在與中國或俄國的大國衝突上取得優勢。<br />\n<br />\n人們往往認定專制政體更常發動突襲，民主政體受限於國際法，難以發起突襲，並非如此。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出中國經濟及軍事力量上的增長驚人，但並非全無弱點：<br />\n<br />\n政經方面<br />\n1.天子執着於國內穩定，置穩定及統一放在一齊之上，亦是政權合法性的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n2.視小數民族威脅國內穩定，例子有西藏及新疆，高壓政策手段惹來獨狼式的反抗及動亂。<br />\n<br />\n3.經濟增長支撐政權合法性，有經濟增長縱使沒有民主亦無妨，此等社會契約沿用至今。<br />\n<br />\n4.大力反貪引起黨內權貴不滿。<br />\n<br />\n軍事外交方面<br />\n1.中國在國家上係一個孤立的強國，文化及政治自成一脈，其架構對列國並無吸引力。一帶一路上的掠奪行為引起各國警惕。中國在南海上的進取使鄰國疏遠。<br />\n<br />\n2.解放軍自1979年中越戰爭後再沒實戰經驗，不同於立國初期，軍方領導有內戰及韓戰經驗。<br />\n<br />\n3.中國依賴海運貿易，有全球最大的貿易船隊，要同時保護貿易、漫長海岸線，南海填海建造又極為脆弱的基地，海軍處於不利局面。<br />\n<br />\n4.依賴馬六甲海峽入口主要石油。<br />\n<br />\n5.解放軍缺乏遠程作戰能力，但在第一島鏈內能極為有效地作戰。<br />\n<br />\n6.兵役制度不佳，義務役兵只需服後兩年，加上又要多次輪調，不利掌握複雜兵器、獲取聯合作戰經驗。<br />\n<br />\n7.軍隊加強中央集權，以領導人為核心，但不利作出及時的決策。<br />\n<br />\n報名建議一系列針對弱點的作戰方向，見附圖（擷取自報告72頁）及報告原文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csis.org/analysis/inflicting-surprise-gaining-competitive-advantage-great-power-conflicts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csis.org%2Fanalysis%2Finflicting-surprise-gaining-competitive-advantage-great-power-conflicts&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGcwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=5f3b872e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csis.org/analysis/inflicting-surprise-gaining-competitive-advantage-great-power-conflicts</a>"},{"pid":"7f2c8aaf4e74017408b37c90da540ccf1f9f066e","tid":2404786,"uid":97078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"講晒出黎姐係點"},{"pid":"c124cf86e51cde3987e0869cb15d83c654062262","tid":2404786,"uid":47042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f2c8aaf4e74017408b37c90da540ccf1f9f066e","tid":2404786,"uid":97078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"講晒出黎姐係點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:54:58.000Z","msg":"震懾<br />\n<br />\n打開口牌無問題，最大問題係打啲佢唔識拆既開口牌<br />\n咁佢咪驚到腳震"},{"pid":"4588a3d5fa7dab161c32bd1b34b3d48b8c3b1b34","tid":2404786,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:57:16.000Z","msg":"LM 待看 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8382cb89bca8f8b78ee5b3e17a7a216f304f9c67","tid":2404786,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:57:56.000Z","msg":"拜登：中美合作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/large/006L3mengy1gncdxptqpzj30ru0fotc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx1.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006L3mengy1gncdxptqpzj30ru0fotc0.jpg&h=401d4063&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3f78dfd043924312e6f6957861f7a2a8099914e","tid":2404786,"uid":370061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:58:55.000Z","msg":"just empty talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c4490fa04947beb77d744d003e549a38940daf","tid":2404786,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"All talks No action Sounds good Doesn&rsquo;t work"},{"pid":"0a34ead5f43cedc2fa96ab1c1277cefa3520bcc0","tid":2404786,"uid":91721,"like"